section.para:
StemmerFactory captures a stemmer configuration once and mints configured Stemmer instances on demand. It is a plain supplier of stemmers, not a BaseToolFactory loaded from a model manifest. The English Snowball factory needs no external data: StemmerFactoryUsageExampleTest asserts the behavior shown here.
StemmerFactory factory = new SnowballStemmerFactory(SnowballStemmer.ALGORITHM.ENGLISH); Stemmer stemmer = factory.newStemmer();
stemmer.stem("running"); // "run" stemmer.stemAll("running"); // ["run"]
